"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">57</A>
<I>Cf.</I> <A HREF="
https://www.perseus.tufts.edu/hopper/text?doc=Perseus:text:1999.01.0160:book=4:chapter=30
	"TARGET="offsite"
